WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.080
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:27.474 --> 00:00:27.885
Thank you for joining us again today.

00:00:48.720 --> 00:00:48.960
We're going to pray tonight; we have a lot to pray about all day today.

00:00:48.960 --> 00:00:57.869
I've had great urgency for what I'm seeing in the spirit based on what we saw last night.

00:00:57.869 --> 00:01:39.240
If anybody was with us last night—and I know we're doing a lot of back-to-back videos, and I know there's a lot of you that don't have time to pray through all those videos because it takes a lot of your day with families and things—I'll give you a little recap of what we prayed over and what the Lord showed us in the spirit.

00:01:45.170 --> 00:01:45.560
We give all the glory to God.

00:01:45.560 --> 00:01:49.874
Brandon is not able to do any of this on his own.

00:01:49.874 --> 00:01:56.204
Everything that I believe the Lord is showing me will prove to be accurate in the future, as you'll see in the news.

00:01:56.204 --> 00:01:59.999
But we don't pray the news; we pray ahead of time.

00:01:59.999 --> 00:02:02.532
We're watchmen; we see in advance.

00:02:02.532 --> 00:02:08.160
And for what we see, it's coming to pass.

00:02:08.160 --> 00:02:13.120
It looks like it for those who are part of my prayer team.

00:02:16.171 --> 00:02:16.629
I want to call you all my elite prayer team.

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:23.359
We have the best of the best prayer warriors.

00:02:23.839 --> 00:02:34.978
The Lord said, 'I've assembled the best prayer warriors of this generation on your prayer team, and you all will pray and change things through prayer.

00:02:34.978 --> 00:02:38.800
' I believe with all my heart that word is coming to pass.

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:45.960
There is a very strong core of you—125,000—that watch and pray, and that's just through this platform alone.

00:02:45.960 --> 00:02:55.771
We have a real solid 125,000 people who join almost every video and pray with us.

00:02:55.771 --> 00:03:00.676
We're so thankful for every single one of you who comes out.

00:03:00.676 --> 00:03:11.782
I would say we have a great group of intercessors, and I'm so thankful for every single one of you.

00:03:21.620 --> 00:03:21.920
We're going to go over what the Lord has shown us over the last video.

00:03:21.920 --> 00:03:27.731
Help me to remember everything because He showed us a lot, and He has my notes.

00:03:27.731 --> 00:03:31.097
First off, I saw something concerning Cuba.

00:03:47.874 --> 00:03:48.309
I saw a beautiful home, white-looking, with some kind of stucco roofs and clay shingles.

00:04:09.140 --> 00:04:09.450
It didn't look like modern-day asphalt shingles; these looked like clay shingles on a mansion in Cuba.

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:22.496
Underneath this mansion were tunnels and passageways that went in all different directions to a bunker.

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:42.230
There was an escape route to a bunker inside the side of a mountain, where tunnels led to a place with an escape route for a really nice boat.

00:04:55.897 --> 00:05:02.939
Then I saw a helicopter take off from the top of the mountain.

00:05:07.234 --> 00:05:11.067
Everything the Lord was showing me was concerning the gray-headed man, the leader of Cuba, Miguel Díaz-Canel.

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:33.920
The Lord said again that He was going to get rid of the Castro name—the Castros, all of them—and that there would basically be a bloodline cleansing of dictatorship out of that land.

00:05:40.400 --> 00:05:47.860
The Lord showed me again trade with Cuba coming with the United States of America.

00:05:53.120 --> 00:06:06.800
It will be like a state where Cuba and America will be friends with new leadership that will come about with Marco Rubio.

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:23.360
I saw Rubio establishing a great Cuba in the days ahead that will bring prosperity and economic stability with a tourist industry.

00:06:23.360 --> 00:06:37.440
I saw resorts opening up on the water and great hotel chains from America going into Cuba, bringing hotels and resorts for holiday travel.

00:06:41.520 --> 00:07:01.120
I saw the cigar industry—though I don't believe in smoking, this is what I saw—with golden band cigars being traded around the world and into America; it was big business.

00:07:01.653 --> 00:07:06.199
On the other side of the island, facing Jamaica, I saw a plant or big business being established.

00:07:13.040 --> 00:07:13.480
I saw American-made cars—Ford, GMC, and Chevrolet—going over to Cuba.

00:07:19.199 --> 00:07:37.240
I don't know if they have a factory there or if they're just buying our automobiles, but I saw F-150 trucks, Ford, and GMC trucks all going to Cuba in the days ahead, with people driving new and used trucks.

00:07:39.337 --> 00:07:39.589
I saw economic growth and stability coming to Cuba again.

00:08:03.016 --> 00:08:09.120
But the Lord said, 'You must pray for what's about to happen in the near future.

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:21.909
' I'm not going to give time frames because the Lord told me this is very soon.

00:08:22.593 --> 00:08:31.199
I saw all this stuff coming specifically in the darkness.

00:08:31.199 --> 00:08:40.205
We must pray tonight for a hedge of protection around people.

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:52.000
Then the vision switched to Iran.

00:08:54.560 --> 00:08:57.670
This was very serious and heavy.

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:11.839
There were things I was hearing because I was caught up, and I could hear the conversation taking place with the man appointed to the Ayatollah committee today, the leader of Iran.

00:09:17.246 --> 00:09:23.982
I heard him underground talking to a man with a white beard and a white turban.

00:09:25.129 --> 00:09:31.252
He was asking this elder, 'Is it time to go ahead with phase two?

00:09:31.252 --> 00:09:37.698
' I saw massive missiles and underground military installations with biological weapons of mass destruction.

00:09:41.627 --> 00:09:54.080
I believe I saw things from Saddam in Iraq from when we went after them for weapons of mass destruction in 2000.

00:09:54.080 --> 00:10:14.989
There was chemical warfare that would make your skin melt off your body with massive boils, and I saw people convulse to the point that their spines snapped.

00:10:14.989 --> 00:10:23.720
I'm just telling you what I saw in the vision.

00:10:23.720 --> 00:10:34.000
I saw that it was used up toward the Damascus area and that part of Israel.

00:10:47.947 --> 00:10:48.222
It was an attack worse than October 7th of four years ago.

00:11:00.420 --> 00:11:00.670
This was an attack plan.

00:11:00.670 --> 00:11:03.977
He asked, 'Do the prophecies line up?

00:11:03.977 --> 00:11:06.219
Are we really there?

00:11:06.219 --> 00:11:14.128
' The Lord allowed me to understand him asking, 'Is it really time for the Mahdi to come?

00:11:14.128 --> 00:11:25.440
' They were discussing the Quran and Muslim prophetic words, looking for the sign of their savior, the Mahdi.

00:11:43.570 --> 00:11:43.920
I heard them discussing how to bring forth this false god, whom we believe is the Antichrist.

00:11:43.920 --> 00:11:54.811
Remember, I told you when the Mahdi comes, it's on Fridays that you're made to worship during the Tribulation, wearing white clothes and using rugs.

00:11:54.811 --> 00:12:07.840
Everyone around the world will be required to look at the man on the screen; he will be the Antichrist.

00:12:07.840 --> 00:12:12.639
I'm telling you, I've seen it.

00:12:39.600 --> 00:12:40.023
On July 6, 2014, I was taken out of my body, and the Lord took me to the Tribulation.

00:12:40.023 --> 00:12:47.783
Whether you believe that or not, I'm telling you what is coming.

00:12:47.783 --> 00:13:00.106
People were on mats on Fridays, and everyone was required to worship the image of this man on a screen in major towns.

00:13:00.106 --> 00:13:01.983
It's at the Vatican.

00:13:01.983 --> 00:13:04.367
It will be all over the place.

00:13:04.367 --> 00:13:13.204
Everyone will go to the Vatican and they will worship the Antichrist there one day.

00:13:13.214 --> 00:13:14.960
I saw it.

00:13:27.170 --> 00:13:27.600
It will be in France.

00:13:34.687 --> 00:13:38.780
It will be in America, in Washington.

00:13:38.780 --> 00:13:40.457
It will be all over the place.

00:13:40.457 --> 00:13:45.839
There will be screens and everybody will be required to worship somebody.

00:13:45.839 --> 00:13:50.079
If you do not, they take your head off.

00:13:50.079 --> 00:14:02.480
I'm telling you that as I was listening to this man talk underground in a bunker, I could see missiles and things around him.

00:14:02.480 --> 00:14:08.459
He was talking about some kind of weapon they had that they believe nobody else had.

00:14:10.959 --> 00:14:18.800
They were talking about a weapon they have that nobody knows they have.

00:14:18.800 --> 00:14:24.160
It was one thing.

00:14:24.160 --> 00:14:29.749
They had one thing and I believe this was a nuclear thing.

00:14:29.749 --> 00:14:45.040
This was something they've developed or they have received from someone else, but it was on a payload on a rocket and I saw him touching the rocket.

00:14:45.760 --> 00:14:48.250
He was talking about this massive thing.

00:14:48.250 --> 00:14:51.657
He was talking to the man with the white beard.

00:14:51.657 --> 00:14:55.770
They were under the ground and they were discussing biblical prophecy there.

00:14:55.770 --> 00:15:01.080
Now, I keep saying biblical prophecy because that's what we do—Quran prophecy, false god prophecy.

00:15:03.440 --> 00:15:09.480
And they were talking about this and they were saying, "Is it time to push the button?

00:15:09.480 --> 00:15:10.860
Is it time?

00:15:10.860 --> 00:15:15.600
Do you believe we're at the time for the Mahdi to come?

00:15:15.600 --> 00:15:24.128
" And they were about to make a decision to try to take out Israel with biological warfare.

00:15:24.128 --> 00:15:26.959
It was chemicals.

00:15:26.959 --> 00:15:31.299
And I saw this and I was praying against this last night.

00:15:31.299 --> 00:15:33.382
That's what we were all praying against.

00:15:33.382 --> 00:15:35.839
This was a major plan.

00:15:35.839 --> 00:15:42.000
And they said, "We have to activate the cells in America.

00:15:42.000 --> 00:15:43.760
It's time.

00:15:43.760 --> 00:15:52.160
" And they were discussing underground, these two men—the man that was pronounced to be the head of Iran today.

00:15:52.160 --> 00:16:02.754
I heard him say, "We must communicate to the terrorists, these cells in America, and activate them.

00:16:02.754 --> 00:16:05.600
Is it time?

00:16:05.600 --> 00:16:08.319
" And he was talking to the man with the white beard.

00:16:08.319 --> 00:16:09.880
I heard this.

00:16:09.880 --> 00:16:11.813
It was very detailed.

00:16:11.813 --> 00:16:16.399
I'm not telling you everything that was said.

00:16:16.399 --> 00:16:21.160
You need to know we're in a time like we've never seen before.

00:16:21.160 --> 00:16:40.100
The Lord said—and this is why the church has to rise up and pray like we've never prayed before—because we understand that Jesus Christ is coming and that our Jesus, our Savior, is coming for the bride.

00:16:40.100 --> 00:16:43.973
But the Lord said, "I'm coming back for a harvest.

00:16:44.426 --> 00:16:46.240
I have long patience.

00:16:46.240 --> 00:16:47.360
" Where's the scripture?

00:16:47.360 --> 00:16:54.550
"I have long patience for the harvest, for the fruit.

00:16:54.560 --> 00:17:09.210
" So when we see all these things coming, the Lord said on September 23rd of last year, we're at a point of no return when the UN voted against Israel and all the things that took place.

00:17:09.210 --> 00:17:18.970
