00:17:23.680 --> 00:17:34.860
" But he said last night, "Not only will you see the wars and the rumors of wars and the things manifesting, but you're going to start to see major events in the earth's crust.

00:17:34.860 --> 00:17:39.600
" And I saw solar flares from our sun pounding our earth.

