00:18:25.644 --> 00:18:26.320
You need to listen to me.

00:18:27.829 --> 00:18:28.862
I'm not trying to scare you.

00:18:28.862 --> 00:18:31.955
No, this is something that we need to pray about.

00:18:31.955 --> 00:18:33.760
I'm not trying to scare you.

00:18:33.760 --> 00:18:38.136
It's like I hear, "We're trying to prepare you.

00:18:38.136 --> 00:18:45.060
" I'm trying to tell you we're in the last of the last days.

00:18:45.060 --> 00:18:58.533
If you see the signs of the times all around you and you have your eyes open and your head's not in the sand like the ostrich, you see where we are.

00:18:58.533 --> 00:19:01.530
Ladies and gentlemen, Jesus Christ is coming.

00:19:01.530 --> 00:19:03.773
He's standing at the door.

00:19:03.773 --> 00:19:05.531
Are you ready to go?

00:19:20.891 --> 00:19:21.177
